{{Databox|en=Sidi Ifni}}Tga '''Ifni''' nɣd '''Sidi Ifni''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: ⵙⵉⴼⵉ ⵉⴼⵏⵉ, s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: سيدي إفني) yat tamdint [[Lmɣrib|tamɣribit]] illan ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Glmim-Asif Nun|Glmim-Asif Nun]], twala i tmazirt [[Sus]] tili ɣ iggi wakal n tqbilt tasusit n [[Ayt Baɛmran]]. Tettyawsan sidi ifni s tgmrt n [[Aslm|islman]].

== Asnmkta ==
Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2014 mas<ref>[http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/ RGPH 2014 - Site HCP]</ref>:

=== Aslmd ===

* Tigmiḍi n taqubbanit (middn lli ur ssin ad aqran wala ad ttaran) : 25.7%
* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli iɣran ar usinan n usmdi nɣd uggar : 13.1%

=== Tadamsa ===

* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli llan ɣ isggasn nnsn n twuri : 45.1%
* Tigmiḍi n tarwuri (middn lli ur ṭṭafn tawuri) : 30.2%
* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli swurin dar lmxzn (nɣ kantin swurin gis) : 28.1%
* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli swurin ɣ uslig (nɣ kantin swurin gis) : 34.4%

